txt.en: 'The palisade may stand, but the timbers are burnt and ready to fall at the slightest touch. It would be better if they were not there at all, for they provide naught but false security. We need to replace the wall, section-by-section, piece-by-piece.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
